Subject: [PATCH v2 12/14] arm64: dts: rockchip: add missing pmic information on Qnap-TS433
Date: Sun, 21 Jul 2024 19:37:21 +0200
Message-Id: <20240721173723.919961-13-heiko@sntech.de>
